<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Gallery_FindingCreations" s="316035">
  <T n="name">0x47272CC3<!--String: "Finding Creations"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_Gallery_2.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:d8c18f8fe7554a0d</T>
      <T n="text">0xDD679603<!--String: "To <b><font color='#199C2C'>find creations</font></b> made by other Simmers, go to the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Gallery tab</font></b> of the Gallery. Let yourself be inspired by their creativity, and find content to add to your own game!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_FindingCreations_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:939fbd9fbfad9450</T>
      <T n="text">0xCCB75818<!--String: "You can use the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Filters</font></b> located on the left side of the screen to refine the content that is being displayed. \n\nFilters such as Popular Now and Most Popular display the creations with the most downloads. You can also narrow your results to just show Households, Lots, or Rooms."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_FIndingCreations_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:939fbd9fbfad9451</T>
      <T n="text">0xD465E177<!--String: "The <b><font color='#199C2C'></b>Search</font></b> bar, found at the top of the screen, allows you to find creations by Item Name, Hashtag, or EA Account ID. \n\nYou can also use the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Trending Hashtags</font></b>, found just below the Search, to see what’s trending among your fellow Simmers!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_FindingCreations_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:939fbd9fbfad9456</T>
      <T n="text">0xCDCF176D<!--String: "Once you’ve found a creation you like, you can select it to open a more <b><font color='#199C2C'>detailed view</font></b>. Here you’ll find more pictures and a description.\n\nIf you like what you see, you can check out more made by the same creator. Click their name to go to their <b><font color='#199C2C'>Profile</font></b>.\n\nYou can also use the <b><font color='#199C2C'>hashtags</font></b> in the description to find other creations with similar themes. "--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_FIndingCreations_5.png">2f7d0004:00000000:939fbd9fbfad9457</T>
      <T n="text">0x60115FE8<!--String: "Upon visiting another player’s Profile, you can view their <b><font color='#199C2C'>Catalog</font></b> of Shared Content and Favorites. \n\nYou can also <b><font color='#199C2C'>Follow</font></b> them, and then they show up your Feed on the News tab whenever they add something new!"--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
  <L n="tags">
    <E>Lesson_Gallery</E>
    <E>Lesson_ChildAccountRestricted</E>
  </L>
